com.koverse.sdk.record.webapp

Interface WebAppRecordConverter


  • public interface WebAppRecordConverter
    Used to provide a new type of download format for data set records. To enable the Koverse web app to offer more types of file types for data set downloads, create a new module by extending AbstractWebAppRecordConverterModule. Implementations report on what type of file they create (as a mime type), a description of their purpose, a short easy to understand name, and methods to write records to an output stream.
